description: It's been awhile since I've put a lesson on youtube.  This one is short and sweet.  Not very difficult but signature to Slim Gaillard's playing.  This intro can work for a blues as well.  Hope you guys like it.  You can always check out my website for other products, as well as performance and clinic schedule.   https://tommyharkenriderguitar.com/
title: Slim Gaillard Rhythm Changes Intro Guitar Lesson by Tommy Harkenrider
fulltitle: Slim Gaillard Rhythm Changes Intro Guitar Lesson by Tommy Harkenrider
